parser

Class DocumentInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • parser.DocumentInfo

  • public class DocumentInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates a new object of type DocumentInfo. It contains the information about the slideshow, including the author, version, the group ID, and a brief comment about the document's content.
    Version:
    2.1
